snippet.title: Buissons - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Buissons will be available february 3rd (3 février), for PC & Mac!
Whishlist the game on STEAM : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1151930/Buissons

Take control of a bush and challenge your friends in a hide and seek game up to 4 players.  Move at night and use the day as an opportunity to observe and beat your opponents. Use the secrets of nature to trap them. Get ready to laugh!

Made by :
Géraud Zucchini https://twitter.com/DrGeraud
Antoine Druaux https://twitter.com/Kilirane
